1
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,480
I heard

2
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,840
Yanzhang

3
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:40,000
requested leave from the court

4
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:42,359
to attend your wedding with Yanyun.

5
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:44,000
He's rushed

6
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,280
all the way back from Shaanxi.

7
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,120
That also shows

8
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:50,719
how much Yanyun values

9
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:53,159
this marriage.

10
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:55,560
I can rest easy now.

11
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:57,120
Nanny Tong.

12
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:57,719
Yes?

13
00:01:57,719 --> 00:01:59,040
Tell everyone to go back.

14
00:01:59,239 --> 00:01:59,879
Got it.

15
00:02:00,879 --> 00:02:02,400
Come with me.

16
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:39,159
This old friend of mine

17
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:41,400
has been stubborn since childhood

18
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:43,800
She hates being talked back to

19
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:47,120
and can't stand people who show off.

20
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,520
Then I'll keep a low profile

21
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,919
and only say

22
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,280
what pleases her.

23
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,639
That's right.

24
00:02:57,919 --> 00:03:00,759
Yanyun has two elder brothers,

25
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,360
both born to concubines.

26
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:03,599
The eldest one

27
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,400
passed away

28
00:03:05,479 --> 00:03:06,599
at 20

29
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,800
from malaria.

30
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:10,080
Yanzhang was

31
00:03:10,199 --> 00:03:12,039
raised by Mrs. Chen

32
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,479
and is highly favored.

33
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,240
He serves as

34
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:18,039
Provincial Administration Commissioner.

35
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:21,000
His wife, born into

36
00:03:21,479 --> 00:03:24,360
the renowned Qin family of Zhending,

37
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,599
has taken charge of

38
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,719
the household after marrying in.

39
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:33,080
Yanzhang's holding office in Shaanxi,

40
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,840
so she has to travel between two places.

41
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:38,439
She may not

42
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,639
be able to run the household forever.

43
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,680
Better to let her stay in charge.

44
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,240
Why?

45
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:50,879
Don't you wanna

46
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:52,560
be the lady in charge?

47
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:56,000
I thought with no say in the household,

48
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,240
people would walk over me.

49
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,439
Now I understand.

50
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,800
Running the household is exhausting

51
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,759
and thankless.

52
00:04:03,759 --> 00:04:04,719
Sometimes you have to

53
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,759
cover the shortfall yourself.

54
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:08,000
I'd rather

55
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,919
put that energy

56
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,919
into my own business.

57
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,599
That's far more worthwhile.

58
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,319
Well said.

59
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,160
You know

60
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,120
better than to fight

61
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:23,240
over household power.

62
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,720
I didn't teach you for nothing.

63
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:30,879
Yanyun has a younger full brother,

64
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:33,000
named Yanwen.

65
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:36,639
He once passed the provincial exams,

66
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:39,560
but for some reason,

67
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:41,800
he never sat for the imperial exams again.

68
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,879
He only handles daily affairs in the manor.

69
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,279
Yanyun once mentioned

70
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:51,079
Yanwen suffers from seizures.

71
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,040
He even

72
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,319
told you that?

73
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,639
Since he

74
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,399
already told you about his family,

75
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:05,519
no need for me to say more.

76
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:06,680
You

77
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,240
probably know as much as I do.

78
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,199
No,

79
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,839
I wanna hear it from you.

80
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,560
You don't find me nagging?

81
00:05:16,279 --> 00:05:17,600
Of course not.

82
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,199
When you tell me these things,

83
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,360
I feel like

84
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,600
I'm still your little girl,

85
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,800
like I have nothing to fear.

86
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:26,800
Even if I make mistakes,

87
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,439
you'll still be there for me.

88
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,639
Silly girl.

89
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,279
You're about to get married.

90
00:05:33,639 --> 00:05:35,279
Yet you still act spoiled.

91
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:38,000
Grandma,

92
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,519
I don't want to leave you.

93
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,279
I couldn't

94
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,560
bear to let you go either.

95
00:05:50,439 --> 00:05:52,680
You're a blessed child.

96
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,000
You and Yanyun

97
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:57,319
shall look after each other

98
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:58,959
and live a happy life.

99
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:14,240
It's raining.

100
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,120
Be extra careful while you work.

101
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,240
Don't break anything.

102
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,879
Anyone who slips up tomorrow

103
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,480
will be in trouble.

104
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:23,800
- Yes.
- Yes.

105
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:31,480
Hyah!

106
00:06:40,399 --> 00:06:41,000
Lord Ye,

107
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,279
what brings you here?

108
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,920
I've brought your Miss a wedding gift.

109
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:45,480
Sir...

110
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,240
This...

111
00:06:51,759 --> 00:06:52,240
Dezhu.

112
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,199
Baoning?

113
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:54,160
Go inform the Chen family.

114
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:54,879
Quick.

115
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:30,920
You just stay here.

116
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:31,959
Yes.

117
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,639
Lord Ye, hold on.

118
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:43,839
Your eyes are so swollen.

119
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,120
You have to stop crying.

120
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,800
With the bridal veil on tomorrow,

121
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:49,079
no one will see me.

122
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:50,560
Miss,

123
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,560
Mr. Chen'll lift your veil eventually.

124
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,759
Lord Ye,

125
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,240
Jinzhao is getting married tomorrow.

126
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:01,439
You're not her close kin.

127
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:03,079
Please don't put

128
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,319
her reputation at risk.

129
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,399
Reputation?

130
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,160
What is there to fear?

131
00:08:13,199 --> 00:08:14,519
Aren't I her uncle?

132
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:17,360
You can't do this!

133
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,439
Xianhuai.

134
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,360
What's that noise?

135
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:33,480
Go.

136
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,360
Have someone bring over a chair.

137
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:38,399
Lord Ye may be displeased.

138
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:40,799
Do you want to cross Chen Yanyun?

139
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,440
Go fetch a chair.

140
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,559
Miss,

141
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,240
sounds like Lord Ye's here.

142
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:49,840
Don't open it.

143
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,279
Are you feeling better?

144
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:21,080
I still remember

145
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:22,919
at my coming-of-age ceremony,

146
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,600
I defied my father

147
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,519
in front of all guests,

148
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,399
and you were the first

149
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,159
to stand up for me.

150
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,279
Even three people can make a model marriage.

151
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:36,559
Well said.

152
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:37,840
You deserve a reward.

153
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:39,879
I've never

154
00:10:41,799 --> 00:10:43,120
forgotten your kindness since then.

155
00:10:45,639 --> 00:10:46,720
Later,

156
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,039
I rode with you

157
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,480
to Sili Hutong.

158
00:10:52,919 --> 00:10:54,240
You taught

159
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:55,600
my father

160
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,480
a lesson,

161
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:59,600
so I could find my place

162
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,080
in that unfamiliar home.

163
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,159
You've

164
00:11:09,639 --> 00:11:11,360
helped me so many times after that too.

165
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:14,600
It wasn't one-sided.

166
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,440
You've done plenty for me too.

167
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,600
Before the rebellion,

168
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:27,080
you rushed back from Tongzhou

169
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,039
to inform me.

170
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,799
It could've cost your life.

171
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:32,799
You're willing to

172
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:33,759
stake your life for me,

173
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,639
and yet you say

174
00:11:38,639 --> 00:11:40,039
you have no feelings for me?

175
00:11:41,879 --> 00:11:42,639
That's different.

176
00:11:42,639 --> 00:11:43,679
How is it different?

177
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,440
Do you blame me

178
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,679
for never proposing to you?

179
00:11:54,559 --> 00:11:55,279
No.

180
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,360
Xian,

181
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:04,159
I'm willing to

182
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,639
risk my life for you,

183
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,120
but love isn't

184
00:12:09,279 --> 00:12:10,720
the only reason one would do that.

185
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,600
Friends do it for each other too.

186
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,639
Friends?

187
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,639
Just friends?

188
00:12:53,039 --> 00:12:53,960
I've got no umbrellas.

189
00:12:54,519 --> 00:12:55,159
It's cold outside.

190
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,320
Put it on.

191
00:13:16,759 --> 00:13:17,679
You might

192
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:19,720
not believe this.

193
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,000
In fact,

194
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:25,080
growing up,

195
00:13:26,159 --> 00:13:27,320
aside from my family,

196
00:13:28,559 --> 00:13:29,679
I never really had any friends.

197
00:13:33,879 --> 00:13:35,200
You're the only one

198
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:38,279
I've ever had.

199
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,240
People say

200
00:13:41,519 --> 00:13:42,919
you're difficult and strange,

201
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,200
but I know

202
00:13:44,639 --> 00:13:45,720
you're not.

203
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:48,440
You're just

204
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,879
at a loss for what to do.

205
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:56,360
I'm the same.

206
00:13:57,279 --> 00:13:58,759
I'm the eldest daughter,

207
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,799
but I had to

208
00:14:00,919 --> 00:14:02,159
leave my parents when I was little.

209
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:06,320
No matter how well others treat me,

210
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,320
there is always

211
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,480
an emptiness inside me.

212
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:16,879
I used to be bad-tempered

213
00:14:17,159 --> 00:14:18,240
and arrogant.

214
00:14:19,799 --> 00:14:21,480
That was only because I was too afraid,

215
00:14:22,679 --> 00:14:24,320
so I acted tough.

216
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:33,879
You don't know

217
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,759
how many times

218
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:38,279
I've looked at you

219
00:14:39,279 --> 00:14:40,799
and felt like I was looking in a mirror,

220
00:14:42,679 --> 00:14:44,279
like I was seeing another version of myself.

221
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,639
Xian,

222
00:14:56,679 --> 00:14:57,840
you are

223
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:59,759
very special to me.

224
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:18,440
But

225
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:22,240
I cannot love you,

226
00:15:24,279 --> 00:15:25,600
because we are the same kind of person,

227
00:15:26,159 --> 00:15:27,720
restless and hurt inside,

228
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:29,080
yet too stubborn

229
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:30,200
to say it.

230
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,000
We pretend to be brave

231
00:15:32,679 --> 00:15:33,960
and say the opposite of what we mean.

232
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:36,320
We long to be cared for

233
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,159
but can never bring ourselves to say it.

234
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:42,679
Xian,

235
00:15:45,279 --> 00:15:46,799
for all 18 years of my life,

236
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:51,000
I've felt tired every single day.

237
00:15:56,159 --> 00:15:57,320
I cannot

238
00:15:58,080 --> 00:16:00,039
be with someone who is just like me.

239
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,600
Then you think marrying Chen Yanyun

240
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:17,720
makes your life easier?

241
00:16:20,919 --> 00:16:22,039
Maybe not,

242
00:16:24,919 --> 00:16:25,759
but

243
00:16:26,679 --> 00:16:27,480
I'm willing.

244
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:33,159
You love him that much?

245
00:16:51,559 --> 00:16:52,279
Mom,

246
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:55,519
look at the words on the screen.

247
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,919
"Fair Days with You".

248
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:01,320
What kind of uncle sent that?

249
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:03,799
His feelings are clearly romantic.

250
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:04,720
Shut up.

251
00:17:05,519 --> 00:17:06,240
You have a death wish?

252
00:17:13,039 --> 00:17:13,759
Mr. Chen.

253
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:19,880
Ma'am, thank you.

254
00:17:20,359 --> 00:17:20,960
It's the least I could do.

255
00:17:22,279 --> 00:17:23,039
Mr. Chen,

256
00:17:24,079 --> 00:17:24,920
they...

257
00:17:25,839 --> 00:17:26,400
I'll handle it.

258
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:27,559
You can go back now.

259
00:17:29,519 --> 00:17:30,240
Yes.

260
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,039
Mr. Chen.

261
00:18:12,039 --> 00:18:12,920
No wonder I couldn't

262
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:14,000
find you anywhere.

263
00:18:16,599 --> 00:18:17,960
I knew

264
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:20,039
you'd be here again.

265
00:18:28,079 --> 00:18:28,799
Guangsheng?

266
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,440
Guangsheng...

267
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:04,720
Ye Xian,

268
00:20:05,839 --> 00:20:07,599
I'll let you off one more time.

269
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:09,359
I know you're young

270
00:20:09,359 --> 00:20:10,160
and reckless.

271
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,400
But remember,

272
00:20:12,319 --> 00:20:13,960
there won't be a next time.

273
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:22,119
[Jinzhao,]

274
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:25,240
[this is my wedding gift for you.]

275
00:20:26,599 --> 00:20:27,720
[With this gift,]

276
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,440
[may every day]

277
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:33,160
[ahead of you]

278
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,200
[be bright and happy.]

279
00:20:38,599 --> 00:20:40,279
[Only from now on, I won't be]

280
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:43,039
[part of your life.]

281
00:20:45,599 --> 00:20:45,960
There.

282
00:20:46,119 --> 00:20:46,799
Higher, higher.

283
00:20:47,559 --> 00:20:48,079
- Like this?
- Yeah.

284
00:20:48,319 --> 00:20:48,759
Move it in.

285
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:49,400
A bit more.

286
00:20:49,559 --> 00:20:50,319
- How about here?
- Right, right.

287
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:51,359
Good, hold it there.

288
00:20:51,359 --> 00:20:51,720
Okay.

289
00:20:55,359 --> 00:20:56,079
Ma'am,

290
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:57,400
will

291
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:58,720
the Chen family

292
00:20:58,720 --> 00:20:59,839
cancel the wedding today?

293
00:21:00,599 --> 00:21:01,319
Nonsense.

294
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:04,519
If they called it off,

295
00:21:05,119 --> 00:21:06,240
it would be admitting

296
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,960
Chen Yanyun lost to Ye Xian.

297
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:09,680
Chen Yanyun

298
00:21:10,279 --> 00:21:11,759
would definitely lose face.

299
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:15,400
But

300
00:21:16,119 --> 00:21:17,559
Jinzhao may have a hard time

301
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,279
after marrying into the Chen family.

302
00:21:20,119 --> 00:21:20,759
Right.

303
00:21:21,119 --> 00:21:21,960
A powerful man

304
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:23,559
like him won't swallow this lightly.

305
00:21:24,119 --> 00:21:25,079
Just wait and see.

306
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:26,799
If Jinzhao

307
00:21:26,799 --> 00:21:28,759
falls out of Mr. Chen's favor,

308
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,319
the two families

309
00:21:31,559 --> 00:21:33,000
will grow distant.

310
00:21:35,559 --> 00:21:36,680
This marriage

311
00:21:37,279 --> 00:21:38,160
looks like

312
00:21:38,359 --> 00:21:39,279
a great honor for us,

313
00:21:40,079 --> 00:21:40,759
but one wrong step

314
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:42,319
could mean trouble.

315
00:21:51,839 --> 00:21:52,440
Go on.

316
00:21:52,599 --> 00:21:53,599
Why did you stop?

317
00:21:55,119 --> 00:21:55,559
Continue.

318
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,279
Chief Minister Liang?

319
00:22:34,519 --> 00:22:35,440
Chancellor Chang?

320
00:22:35,759 --> 00:22:36,559
Dezhao.

321
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:38,839
Mr. He?

322
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:40,759
Quick.

323
00:22:41,079 --> 00:22:42,519
Strike up the music!

324
00:22:42,519 --> 00:22:43,079
Now!

325
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:44,119
- Louder!
- Come on!

326
00:22:46,160 --> 00:22:48,200
Hair combed, hearts united as one.

327
00:22:50,319 --> 00:22:51,559
Then I'll

328
00:22:51,759 --> 00:22:53,559
wait outside.

329
00:22:53,839 --> 00:22:54,880
Thanks, grandma.

330
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:20,920
You look gorgeous.

331
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,440
After all the drama last night,

332
00:23:23,799 --> 00:23:25,279
she's still this calm?

333
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:28,160
You have to leave if you keep

334
00:23:28,319 --> 00:23:28,960
talking nonsense.

335
00:23:33,559 --> 00:23:34,400
Once she's married off,

336
00:23:34,559 --> 00:23:35,400
no one can protect you.

337
00:23:44,039 --> 00:23:45,319
Has the bridal procession arrived?

338
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:46,200
Yes.

339
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:48,440
Who came with the groom?

340
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:49,960
Many high-ranking officials.

341
00:23:50,079 --> 00:23:50,960
Along with Mr. Chen,

342
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,440
the Chancellor of Hanlin Academy,

343
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:53,680
and Vice Minister of Personnel.

344
00:23:53,839 --> 00:23:54,319
Oh,

345
00:23:54,440 --> 00:23:55,559
Grand Secretary He's younger brother

346
00:23:55,559 --> 00:23:56,119
came too.

347
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:57,920
His title is Daily something.

348
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:00,079
Daily Lecturer.

349
00:24:01,319 --> 00:24:03,119
His Majesty's right-hand man,

350
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:04,640
a future Grand Secretary.

351
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:07,119
With so many important figures present,

352
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:08,759
looks like everything's fine.

353
00:24:09,119 --> 00:24:09,920
It's fine.

354
00:24:10,279 --> 00:24:11,759
Mr. Deyuan told you to go to the front hall.

355
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:13,559
All right.

356
00:24:13,559 --> 00:24:14,119
- I'm coming.
- Careful.

357
00:24:14,119 --> 00:24:14,839
Mind your step.

358
00:25:14,519 --> 00:25:15,279
[Mom,]

359
00:25:16,759 --> 00:25:18,119
[it's my wedding day today.]

360
00:25:20,079 --> 00:25:21,799
[I feared I'd follow your painful path.]

361
00:25:22,799 --> 00:25:24,119
[I was afraid of falling in love]

362
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:26,079
[and ending up heartbroken.]

363
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,599
[But somehow,]

364
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,680
[I still want to take a shot.]

365
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:33,759
[Luckily,]

366
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,240
[he is not like the others.]

367
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:38,359
[He truly listens to me]

368
00:25:39,359 --> 00:25:40,319
[and keeps my likes]

369
00:25:40,319 --> 00:25:41,480
[and dislikes in mind.]

370
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:44,440
[Mom,]

371
00:25:45,960 --> 00:25:47,759
[I will live the kind of life]

372
00:25:47,759 --> 00:25:49,119
[you once hoped for.]

373
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:56,279
The bride has arrived!

374
00:26:47,599 --> 00:26:50,119
Bow goodbye to the elders!

375
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:04,359
Second bow.

376
00:27:09,799 --> 00:27:11,079
Third bow.

377
00:27:35,559 --> 00:27:36,839
Fourth bow.

378
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:50,440
The bride leaves home!

379
00:29:30,960 --> 00:29:32,240
On this auspicious day,

380
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:35,240
Chen Yanyun, Grand Secretary,

381
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:38,480
marries Gu Jinzhao,

382
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:39,599
the legitimate daughter

383
00:29:39,799 --> 00:29:41,160
of Gu Dezhao.

384
00:29:41,359 --> 00:29:43,400
Thus, the Chen and Gu families are kin.

385
00:29:43,839 --> 00:29:46,359
The bridal sedan chair comes amid festive music.

386
00:29:46,759 --> 00:29:48,680
All folks along the way

387
00:29:49,000 --> 00:29:51,480
are welcome to share in this joy.

388
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:54,039
Let us bless newlyweds with love, harmony,

389
00:29:54,519 --> 00:29:56,240
longevity, and prosperity.

390
00:30:46,039 --> 00:30:47,559
[Lord Changxing passed away?]

391
00:30:57,039 --> 00:30:57,720
What's the matter?

392
00:30:58,319 --> 00:30:59,759
There's a funeral procession ahead.

393
00:31:00,759 --> 00:31:01,640
The dead deserve respect.

394
00:31:02,599 --> 00:31:03,599
Let's make way for them.

395
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:06,799
Mr. Chen'll take care of it.

396
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:23,880
Make way.

397
00:31:30,039 --> 00:31:30,720
Step aside.

398
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:14,160
Miss,

399
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:16,000
they've made way for us.

400
00:32:20,319 --> 00:32:21,759
I feel bad about this.

401
00:32:30,039 --> 00:32:30,759
Hyah.

402
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:03,599
Let's go.

403
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:52,599
Bow to Heaven and Earth.

404
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:03,360
Bow to the elders.

405
00:35:23,519 --> 00:35:25,960
Bow to each other.

406
00:35:38,960 --> 00:35:40,880
Imperial Decree arrives!

407
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:45,920
By the Mandate of Heaven, the Emperor

408
00:35:45,920 --> 00:35:46,840
decrees.

409
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:49,760
I, having received

410
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:51,239
the charge to govern under Heaven,

411
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:53,559
revere rites and order

412
00:35:53,639 --> 00:35:55,960
and commend virtue and merit.

413
00:35:56,239 --> 00:35:58,239
The regulation of the household

414
00:35:58,239 --> 00:35:59,760
is the key of social harmony.

415
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:01,800
A woman's honor follows her husband's rank.

416
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:03,760
By the law of the state,

417
00:36:04,079 --> 00:36:05,440
Lady Gu, wife of Chen Yanyun,

418
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,639
Grand Secretary of the East Hall

419
00:36:06,639 --> 00:36:08,920
and Left Vice Minister of Revenue,

420
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,400
has done good for the people

421
00:36:10,559 --> 00:36:12,159
and possesses a noble character.

422
00:36:12,360 --> 00:36:14,840
I hereby confer upon her

423
00:36:15,119 --> 00:36:17,280
the title of Second Rank Madam

424
00:36:17,519 --> 00:36:19,559
and hope her stand as

425
00:36:19,559 --> 00:36:21,119
a lasting example of virtue.

426
00:36:21,559 --> 00:36:23,159
By the imperial command.

427
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:27,880
Long live His Majesty!

428
00:36:36,639 --> 00:36:38,559
Mrs. Chen, receive the decree.

429
00:36:39,119 --> 00:36:39,960
Thank

430
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:42,119
His Majesty for his grace.

431
00:36:58,719 --> 00:36:59,280
By custom,

432
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:00,880
only when officials achieve great merit,

433
00:37:01,079 --> 00:37:02,280
can their wives be granted titles.

434
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:05,119
Yet His Majesty bestowed this honor

435
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,760
on Gu Jinzhao on Yanyun's wedding.

436
00:37:08,039 --> 00:37:10,039
This is truly unprecedented.

437
00:37:11,039 --> 00:37:12,360
Yanyun has been working hard.

438
00:37:13,039 --> 00:37:14,519
His Majesty trusts and values him.

439
00:37:16,519 --> 00:37:17,559
As for Gu Jinzhao,

440
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,519
hope she is worthy of this honor.

441
00:37:31,079 --> 00:37:32,880
That phoenix crown is so heavy.

442
00:37:33,679 --> 00:37:34,760
It nearly broke my neck.

443
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:36,360
Thank goodness you

444
00:37:36,440 --> 00:37:37,679
