451
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:54,840
Perhaps nervous about getting married?

452
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,440
It's not that.

453
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,480
Earlier when we passed

454
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:00,480
