455
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:01,960
did you see

456
00:38:02,079 --> 00:38:02,880
which family it was?

457
00:38:03,159 --> 00:38:04,559
I feared it might bring bad luck,

458
00:38:04,719 --> 00:38:05,679
so I didn't look closely at all.

459
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:07,719
All I saw were people dressed in white.

460
00:38:10,599 --> 00:38:11,920
I thought

461
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:14,000
I heard Xian's voice.

462
00:38:14,440 --> 00:38:14,559
Really?

463
00:38:16,159 --> 00:38:17,480
But I didn't see him.

464
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:20,320
Miss,

465
00:38:21,519 --> 00:38:22,880
you're probably overthinking it.

466
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,000
Didn't

467
00:38:24,079 --> 00:38:24,800
Lord Ye

468
00:38:24,800 --> 00:38:25,800
come to see you last night?

469
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:28,960
Ma'am?

470
00:38:35,039 --> 00:38:36,440
In case you're hungry,

471
00:38:36,639 --> 00:38:38,679
Mr. Chen had us bring these dishes over.

472
00:38:41,039 --> 00:38:42,159
- Come on.
- Have a drink.

473
00:38:42,159 --> 00:38:43,000
Thank you for

474
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:43,840
coming in person.

475
00:38:44,679 --> 00:38:45,280
Allow me

476
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:46,519
to raise a toast to you all.

477
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:48,119
- Congrats.
- Congrats.

478
00:38:48,119 --> 00:38:49,320
Congratulations.

479
00:38:51,519 --> 00:38:52,360
Cheers.

480
00:38:54,119 --> 00:38:55,039
- Congrats.
- Congrats.

481
00:38:55,039 --> 00:38:55,800
Congratulations.

482
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,880
- Congrats.
- Congrats.

483
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:24,800
Miss, this dish is so good!

484
00:39:26,199 --> 00:39:28,000
Then have some more.

485
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:33,239
I think

486
00:39:33,639 --> 00:39:34,400
you're right.

487
00:39:35,119 --> 00:39:37,239
Xian came to see me last night.

488
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:39,159
It couldn't have been his family.

489
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:40,840
Miss, I think

490
00:39:41,159 --> 00:39:42,440
you should be worried

491
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:43,960
about Mr. Chen instead.

492
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:45,840
Yanyun?

493
00:39:46,239 --> 00:39:46,920
Why?

494
00:39:47,519 --> 00:39:48,440
After

495
00:39:48,679 --> 00:39:49,719
what happened last night,

496
00:39:50,119 --> 00:39:52,039
aren't you afraid he's angry?

497
00:39:53,960 --> 00:39:55,079
Angry?

498
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:57,480
Maybe a little,

499
00:39:58,039 --> 00:39:59,800
but not at me.

500
00:40:00,599 --> 00:40:02,239
You're enjoying the dishes he sent

501
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:03,880
and still think he's petty?

502
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:06,760
That's true.

503
00:40:08,199 --> 00:40:09,719
I heard the servants say

504
00:40:10,079 --> 00:40:11,800
Mr. Chen's very considerate.

505
00:40:13,079 --> 00:40:14,320
He's sent all these

506
00:40:14,320 --> 00:40:15,679
