512
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:27,199
There are a lot of guests today.

513
00:40:27,360 --> 00:40:28,320
Don't let him drink too much,

514
00:40:28,599 --> 00:40:30,000
and send over the hangover soup.

515
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:30,920
Got it.

516
00:40:55,559 --> 00:40:56,199
Congratulations.

517
00:40:57,079 --> 00:40:57,920
Thanks, Master.

518
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:02,519
Let's drink.

519
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:04,079
Cheers.

520
