525
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:21,840
That's no good.

526
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:28,119
Lord Changxing

527
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:29,599
is finally dead.

528
00:41:29,599 --> 00:41:32,239
How could I let Ye Xian inherit the title?

529
00:41:36,119 --> 00:41:37,880
I heard he caused you

530
00:41:38,159 --> 00:41:39,519
