531
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:43,039
He was just desperate.

532
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:44,159
It's nothing.

533
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:47,440
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

534
00:41:53,360 --> 00:41:54,599
Come on, another round.

535
00:41:55,920 --> 00:41:56,480
He...

536
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:59,800
You've rested at home long enough.

537
00:42:00,360 --> 00:42:02,800
Return to your post in a few days.

538
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:04,679
Great.

539
00:42:04,679 --> 00:42:05,599
Yanyun, come on.

540
00:42:09,559 --> 00:42:10,320
Thanks, Master.

541
00:42:11,239 --> 00:42:12,599
Hailian truly

542
00:42:12,800 --> 00:42:14,280
values Yanyun.

543
00:42:18,119 --> 00:42:18,480
Enough talk.

544
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:19,480
Let's have a drink.

545
00:42:20,159 --> 00:42:20,800
Come on.

546
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:26,599
Master,

547
00:42:26,840 --> 00:42:27,880
I owe you everything.

548
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,960
I can never repay it.

549
00:42:30,519 --> 00:42:31,960
You're my student.

550
00:42:32,320 --> 00:42:32,960
No need for formality.

551
00:42:33,239 --> 00:42:33,559
Let's drink.

552
00:42:34,480 --> 00:42:34,760
Cheers.

553
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:35,440
Bottoms up.

554
00:42:35,719 --> 00:42:36,599
- Cheers.
- Come on.

555
00:42:36,719 --> 00:42:37,599
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

556
00:42:39,119 --> 00:42:39,920
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

557
00:42:39,920 --> 00:42:40,480
Cheers.

558
00:42:41,960 --> 00:42:42,760
Great wine.

559
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:44,719
Let's get drunk tonight.

560
00:42:47,199 --> 00:42:48,480
Looks like something

561
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,280
is on your mind.

562
00:42:52,239 --> 00:42:52,679
No,

563
00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:54,960
I'm just

564
00:42:56,639 --> 00:42:57,280
happy.

565
00:42:58,639 --> 00:42:59,280
Happy?

566
00:43:00,119 --> 00:43:01,360
You don't look happy to me.

567
00:43:16,079 --> 00:43:16,599
Xuanqing?

568
00:43:18,679 --> 00:43:19,760
Just ignore him.

569
00:43:19,920 --> 00:43:20,400
Let's keep drinking.

570
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:20,960
Let's continue.

571
00:43:20,960 --> 00:43:21,519
[Raise your cups.]

572
00:43:21,760 --> 00:43:22,480
[Come on, cheers.]

573
00:43:32,639 --> 00:43:33,599
Jinzhao.
